#

Cedar Plank Grilled Salmon with Honey-Mustard Glaze

$25.99
350 kcal

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

FishGrillingSummerHealthy

Description

Juicy salmon infused with smoky cedar flavor, complemented by a sweet and tangy honey-mustard glaze.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 1 lb
  • Cedar plank: 1
  • Honey: 2 tbsp
  • Dijon mustard: 1 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • Lemon juice: 1 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh dill: for garnish
